title: New PS Plus Titles For October 2023 Leaked - IGN Daily Fix
description:
In today's Daily Fix:
It's almost a new month and new PS Plus games are right around the corner. If you can't wait for Sony to reveal what they are, well, a partial list has leaked. According to billbil-kun of Dealabs, PS Plus Essentials subscribers will be getting The Callisto Protocol, Farming Simulator 22, and another game for free. The Callisto Protocol is a sci-fi survival horror game in the vein of Dead Space, and Farming Simulator is...a farming simulator, but it's got a big update coming in November, so now is the perfect time to get your farm up and running. We don't know what that third game is, but expect Sony to make an announcement soon. In Nintendo Switch news, get this: Red Dead Redemption 2 could be coming to the hybrid console. A rating for a Switch version was spotted on the Brazilian government's website, but Rockstar has not made any announcements about a new version. description: What makes Insomniac’s Spider-Man 2 feel next-gen? The Beyond crew discuss the gameplay mechanics of Spider-Man 2, the expansive world in which you take control of Miles Morales and Peter Parker’s #SpiderMan in #Spiderman2, the unique combat system you can experience in the upcoming Insomniac sequel to Spider-Man, as well as the overall story you will be immersed in when Spider-Man 2 releases.

title: Rainbow Six Siege x Halo - Official Elite Sledge Crossover Trailer
description: Watch the trailer for the Rainbow Six Siege x Elite Sledge Halo crossover, which brings an Elite set for Sledge that outfits him in the armor of the Master Chief. The Elite set features the Spartan-117 headgear and uniform inspired by the Master Chief’s armor in Halo Infinite, as well as a gadget skin that reimagines Sledge’s breaching hammer as a Banished Gravity Hammer. Additionally, there are weapon skins for Sledge’s primary (M590A1 shotgun and L825A2 assault rifle) and secondary (P226 MK25 pistol) weapons, as well as Operator cards, a victory celebration, and the Cortana Chibi charm.

title: Copycat – Official Announcement Trailer
description: Welcome to the playable-cat-game renaissance! Copycat is a narrative adventure game in which you play as a recently adopted shelter cat who has her place in her humans' household stolen by, as the name implies, a copycat. It's in development for PC, PlayStation, Xbox, Nintendo Switch, and Mac.

title: Gran Turismo - Exclusive Official 10 Minute Clip (2023) David Harbour, Orlando Bloom, Archie Madekwe
description:
Based on the true story of Jann Mardenborough and the PlayStation Studios games, the film is the ultimate wish-fulfillment tale of a teenage Gran Turismo player whose gaming skills won a series of Nissan competitions to become an actual professional racecar driver. The Neill Blomkamp-directed movie stars David Harbour, Orlando Bloom, Archie Madekwe, Darren Barnet, Geri Halliwell Horner, and Djimon Hounsou. Gran Turismo is available to buy or rent now on digital and in theaters.

#IGN

title: Harvest Moon: The Winds of Anthos - Official Launch Trailer
description: Harvest Moon: The Winds of Anthos is a new RPG adventure farming simulation game within the Harvest Moon franchise developed by Appci Inc. and Natsume Inc. Players can explore the wide world of Anthos with the help of your inventor friend Doc Jr. and many other characters. The ultimate objective is to bring the Harvest Goddess and the Harvest Sprites back to life along with reconnecting the villages of Anthos once again. The game is fitted with a huge map, new graphic style, updated mechanics, and more for players to enjoy. Harvest Moon: The Winds of Anthos is available now for PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox, Nintendo Switch, and PC.
